					{
						"contentfulId": "6HGUz1pki8q1uj2j3GnUAt",
						"title": "Partnership Overview",
						"copy": "Databricks' Delta Sharing, an open protocol for secure data sharing, seamlessly integrates with Cloudflare R2, Cloudflare's distributed object storage solution with zero egress fees. This integration empowers data teams to share live data sets without complex ETL or costly replication. Joint customers can securely share up-to-date data with partners, suppliers, and lines of business, ensuring security and privacy. By eliminating unexpected egress fees, this integration offers a reliable and cost-effective solution for seamless data sharing.\n\nFind more information on Databricks' [website](https://www.databricks.com/product/delta-sharing).\n",
